ications to the RH code allowing straightforward inclusion of transition\nregion and coronal irradiation in flares.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 14 Aug 2019 20:01:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 29 Sep 2019 16:45:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-02"}
