alent martingale measure via the Esscher transform. Because of the absence\nof traded crypto options we could not compare the prices obtained from our\nvaluation model to market prices. Yet, we can claim that if such options on\ncrypto assets are introduced, they should follow closely our theoretical prices\nafter adjusting for market frictions and design feature nuances.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Aug 2019 04:55:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-15"}
