attempt experiment\nreconstruction and cross-validation of effectiveness, efficiency, and results\nof the state of the art methods. When training and testing classifiers using\nsolely code-sections from executable binary files, all our classifiers\nperformed equally well achieving over 98\\% accuracy. The results are consistent\nand comparable with the current state of the art, hence supports the general\nvalidity of the algorithms\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Aug 2019 08:49:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-24"}
