les to fine-grid solution. We present numerical results for\nseveral porous media applications, including two-phase flow and transport.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Aug 2019 15:31:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 2 Sep 2019 10:01:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-04"}
